&lt;p&gt;You’ll also help the team work in a modern way, including practical use of AI where it speeds up exploration and delivery, with standards that keep the product coherent and responsible.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
